            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Τίτος <lb n="2"/>καὶ Ἐλπὶ<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied> <lb n="3"/>Νεικοπο<lb break="no" n="4"/>λεῖται εὐχα<lb break="no" n="5"/>ριστήρι<supplied reason="lost">ον</supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Τίτος κα<supplied reason="lost">ὶ</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">Ἐ</supplied>λπὶς Νει<lb break="no" n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">κ</supplied>οπολεῖ<lb break="no" n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>αι ε&amp;lt;ὐ&amp;gt;χαρι<supplied reason="lost">σ</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>ήριον
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): druckt nur Τίτος Νεικοπολείτης.</p>
            </div>
